########################################
# Unreal Engine - Source Only Repository
########################################

# --- 기본 정책 ---
# 기본적으로 전부 무시
*

# --- Git 관련 파일은 허용 ---
!.gitignore
!.gitattributes

# --- Unreal 프로젝트 필수 파일 허용 ---
!*.uproject

# --- Source 코드만 허용 ---
!Source/
!Source/**

########################################
# 이하: 명시적 무시 (안전망)
########################################

# IDE / Editor
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sln
*.suo
*.opensdf
*.sdf
*.VC.db
*.VC.opendb
.vsconfig

# Unreal Generated
Binaries/
Intermediate/
Saved/
DerivedDataCache/
Build/

# Plugins (Source만 허용, 나머지 차단)
Plugins/**
!Plugins/**/Source/
!Plugins/**/Source/**

# Asset / Content (전부 제외)
Content/
*.uasset
*.umap
*_BuiltData.uasset

# Logs / Cache
*.log

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
